                        <a href="#submission-controller" class="toc-link"><i class="bi bi-send-check"></i> Submission Controller</a>
                        <a href="#services" class="toc-link"><i class="bi bi-box"></i> Services</a>
                        <a href="#data-models" class="toc-link"><i class="bi bi-database"></i> Data Models</a>
                        <a href="#permissions" class="toc-link"><i class="bi bi-key"></i> Permissions</a>
                        <a href="#review-workflow" class="toc-link"><i class="bi bi-arrow-repeat"></i> Review Workflow</a>
                        <a href="#audit-system" class="toc-link"><i class="bi bi-journal-text"></i> Audit System</a>
                        <a href="#data-upload" class="toc-link"><i class="bi bi-cloud-upload"></i> Data Upload</a>
                        <a href="#configuration" class="toc-link"><i class="bi bi-sliders"></i> Configuration</a>
                        <a href="#file-reference" class="toc-link"><i class="bi bi-folder2-open"></i> File Reference</a>
                        <a href="#default-credentials" class="toc-link"><i class="bi bi-person-lock"></i> Default Credentials</a>
                    </nav>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Main Content -->
        <div class="col-lg-9">

            <!-- 1. Architecture Overview -->
            <section id="architecture" class="guide-section">
                <h2>
                    <span class="section-icon"><i class="bi bi-diagram-2"></i></span>
                    Architecture Overview
                </h2>
                <p>
                    ROSRA V2 is an ASP.NET Core 8 MVC application using Entity Framework Core with SQL Server.
                    The admin and review subsystem is built on ASP.NET Identity with a custom permission layer.
                </p>

                <h3>Technology Stack</h3>
                <table class="guide-table">
                    <thead><tr><th>Component</th><th>Technology</th></tr></thead>
                    <tbody>
                        <tr><td>Framework</td><td>.NET 8 / ASP.NET Core MVC</td></tr>
                        <tr><td>Database</td><td>SQL Server (EF Core with retry-on-failure)</td></tr>
                        <tr><td>Authentication</td><td>ASP.NET Identity with cookie auth</td></tr>
                        <tr><td>Authorization</td><td>Role-based + custom permission handler</td></tr>
                        <tr><td>Session</td><td>In-memory distributed cache (30-min timeout)</td></tr>
                        <tr><td>PDF Generation</td><td>QuestPDF</td></tr>
                        <tr><td>Excel Export</td><td>ClosedXML</td></tr>
                        <tr><td>Localization</td><td>RESX resources (en, fr, es)</td></tr>
                    </tbody>
                </table>

                <h3>Key Layers</h3>
                <table class="guide-table">
                    <thead><tr><th>Layer</th><th>Files</th><th>Responsibility</th></tr></thead>
                    <tbody>
                        <tr>
                            <td><strong>Controllers</strong></td>
                            <td><span class="file-path"><i class="bi bi-file-code"></i> AdminController.cs</span> <span class="file-path"><i class="bi bi-file-code"></i> SubmissionController.cs</span></td>
                            <td>HTTP routing, request validation, view model assembly</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td><strong>Services</strong></td>
                            <td><span class="file-path"><i class="bi bi-file-code"></i> SubmissionService.cs</span> <span class="file-path"><i class="bi bi-file-code"></i> ValidationService.cs</span></td>
                            <td>Business logic for submission workflow and validation</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td><strong>Authorization</strong></td>
                            <td><span class="file-path"><i class="bi bi-file-code"></i> PermissionAuthorizationHandler.cs</span></td>
                            <td>Custom permission checks with 5-minute caching</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td><strong>Data</strong></td>
                            <td><span class="file-path"><i class="bi bi-file-code"></i> ApplicationDbContext.cs</span> <span class="file-path"><i class="bi bi-file-code"></i> DbInitializer.cs</span></td>
                            <td>EF Core context with automatic audit logging in SaveChangesAsync</td>
                        </tr>
                    </tbody>
                </table>
            </section>

            <!-- 2. Authorization System -->
            <section id="auth-system" class="guide-section">
                <h2>
                    <span class="section-icon"><i class="bi bi-shield-check"></i></span>
                    Authorization System
                </h2>
                <p>
                    The app uses a <strong>two-tier authorization model</strong>: Identity roles for coarse access control,
                    and a custom permission system for granular feature gating.
                </p>

                <h3>How It Works</h3>
                <ol>
                    <li>User authenticates via ASP.NET Identity (cookie-based).</li>
                    <li>Roles (<code class="code-inline">Admin</code>, <code class="code-inline">User</code>, <code class="code-inline">Reviewer</code>) control top-level access on controllers.</li>
                    <li>Each role has assigned <strong>Permissions</strong> via the <code class="code-inline">RolePermissions</code> junction table.</li>
                    <li>The <code class="code-inline">PermissionAuthorizationHandler</code> resolves the user's effective permissions at runtime.</li>
                    <li>Permissions are <strong>cached in memory for 5 minutes</strong> per user (key: <code class="code-inline">user_permissions_{userId}</code>).</li>
                </ol>

                <h3>PermissionAuthorizationHandler Flow</h3>
                <div class="code-block">
<span class="cm">// Simplified flow</span>
<span class="kw">1.</span> Check user is authenticated
<span class="kw">2.</span> Look up cache: <span class="str">"user_permissions_{userId}"</span>
<span class="kw">3.</span> If not cached:
   a. Get user roles via UserManager
   b. Query <span class="type">RolePermissions</span> for all role IDs
   c. Extract permission name set
   d. Cache with <span class="num">5-minute</span> TTL
<span class="kw">4.</span> If required permission in set &rarr; <span class="fn">context.Succeed()</span>
                </div>

                <h3>Using Permissions on Actions</h3>
                <div class="code-block">
<span class="cm">// Role-based (coarse)</span>
[<span class="type">Authorize</span>(Roles = <span class="str">"Admin"</span>)]
<span class="kw">public</span> IActionResult Users() { ... }

<span class="cm">// Permission-based (granular)</span>
[<span class="type">RequirePermission</span>(<span class="str">"ViewReports"</span>)]
<span class="kw">public</span> IActionResult AllReports() { ... }
                </div>

                <div class="dev-warning">
                    <i class="bi bi-exclamation-triangle"></i>
                    <strong>Cache Note:</strong> When a user's role permissions change, the old permissions remain active for up to 5 minutes.
                    To force a refresh, clear the cache key <code class="code-inline">user_permissions_{userId}</code>.
                </div>
            </section>

            <!-- 3. Admin Controller -->
            <section id="admin-controller" class="guide-section">
                <h2>
                    <span class="section-icon"><i class="bi bi-gear"></i></span>
                    Admin Controller
                </h2>
                <p>
                    <span class="file-path"><i class="bi bi-file-code"></i> Controllers/AdminController.cs</span>
                    &mdash; All actions require <code class="code-inline">[Authorize(Roles = "Admin")]</code>.
                </p>

                <h3>Route Reference</h3>
                <table class="guide-table">
                    <thead><tr><th>Method</th><th>Route</th><th>Purpose</th></tr></thead>
                    <tbody>
                        <tr><td><span class="route-method route-get">GET</span></td><td><code class="code-inline">/Admin/Index</code></td><td>Dashboard with KPIs and paginated report table (25/page)</td></tr>
                        <tr><td><span class="route-method route-get">GET</span></td><td><code class="code-inline">/Admin/AllReports</code></td><td>Card-based view of all reports with active/archived tabs (12/page)</td></tr>
                        <tr><td><span class="route-method route-get">GET</span></td><td><code class="code-inline">/Admin/DeletedReports</code></td><td>Soft-deleted reports (uses <code class="code-inline">IgnoreQueryFilters()</code>)</td></tr>
                        <tr><td><span class="route-method route-post">POST</span></td><td><code class="code-inline">/Admin/PermanentlyDeleteReport</code></td><td>Hard-delete from database (irreversible)</td></tr>
                        <tr><td><span class="route-method route-post">POST</span></td><td><code class="code-inline">/Admin/RestoreReport</code></td><td>Clears <code class="code-inline">IsDeleted</code>, <code class="code-inline">DeletedAt</code>, <code class="code-inline">DeletedByUserId</code></td></tr>
                        <tr><td><span class="route-method route-get">GET</span></td><td><code class="code-inline">/Admin/Users</code></td><td>User list with search, role filter, status filter</td></tr>
                        <tr><td><span class="route-method route-get">GET</span></td><td><code class="code-inline">/Admin/UserDetails/{id}</code></td><td>Individual user profile with role management</td></tr>
                        <tr><td><span class="route-method route-post">POST</span></td><td><code class="code-inline">/Admin/ToggleUserStatus</code></td><td>Activate/deactivate user via <code class="code-inline">LockoutEnd</code></td></tr>
                        <tr><td><span class="route-method route-post">POST</span></td><td><code class="code-inline">/Admin/AddUserToRole</code></td><td>Assign role + audit log entry</td></tr>
                        <tr><td><span class="route-method route-post">POST</span></td><td><code class="code-inline">/Admin/RemoveUserFromRole</code></td><td>Unassign role + audit log entry</td></tr>
                        <tr><td><span class="route-method route-get">GET</span></td><td><code class="code-inline">/Admin/CreateRole</code></td><td>Role creation form with permission checkboxes</td></tr>
                        <tr><td><span class="route-method route-post">POST</span></td><td><code class="code-inline">/Admin/CreateRole</code></td><td>Create role + assign permissions via <code class="code-inline">RolePermissions</code></td></tr>
                        <tr><td><span class="route-method route-post">POST</span></td><td><code class="code-inline">/Admin/DeleteRole</code></td><td>Delete role (blocked if users assigned or system role)</td></tr>
                        <tr><td><span class="route-method route-get">GET</span></td><td><code class="code-inline">/Admin/EditRolePermissions/{id}</code></td><td>Edit permissions for existing role</td></tr>
                        <tr><td><span class="route-method route-post">POST</span></td><td><code class="code-inline">/Admin/UpdateRolePermissions</code></td><td>Replace all role permissions (delete + re-insert)</td></tr>
                        <tr><td><span class="route-method route-get">GET</span></td><td><code class="code-inline">/Admin/AuditLog</code></td><td>Paginated audit trail (50/page) with action/entity filters</td></tr>
                        <tr><td><span class="route-method route-get">GET</span></td><td><code class="code-inline">/Admin/DataUpload</code></td><td>CSV upload form</td></tr>
                        <tr><td><span class="route-method route-post">POST</span></td><td><code class="code-inline">/Admin/UploadPeerSNGData</code></td><td>Parse and import Peer SNG CSV</td></tr>
                        <tr><td><span class="route-method route-post">POST</span></td><td><code class="code-inline">/Admin/UploadCountryData</code></td><td>Parse and import Country data CSV (16 columns)</td></tr>
                    </tbody>
                </table>

                <h3>User Status Logic</h3>
                <div class="code-block">
<span class="cm">// Active: not locked or lockout expired</span>
<span class="kw">bool</span> isActive = !user.LockoutEnabled
    || user.LockoutEnd == <span class="kw">null</span>
    || user.LockoutEnd < DateTimeOffset.UtcNow;

<span class="cm">// Deactivate: lock until year 2100</span>
user.LockoutEnabled = <span class="kw">true</span>;
user.LockoutEnd = <span class="kw">new</span> DateTimeOffset(<span class="num">2100</span>, <span class="num">1</span>, <span class="num">1</span>, ...);

<span class="cm">// Activate: clear lockout</span>
user.LockoutEnd = <span class="kw">null</span>;
user.LockoutEnabled = <span class="kw">false</span>;
                </div>

                <h3>Role Deletion Guards</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>System roles <code class="code-inline">Admin</code> and <code class="code-inline">User</code> cannot be deleted.</li>
                    <li>Roles with assigned users cannot be deleted &mdash; remove all users first.</li>
                </ul>
            </section>

            <!-- 4. Submission Controller -->
            <section id="submission-controller" class="guide-section">
                <h2>
                    <span class="section-icon"><i class="bi bi-send-check"></i></span>
                    Submission Controller
                </h2>
                <p>
                    <span class="file-path"><i class="bi bi-file-code"></i> Controllers/SubmissionController.cs</span>
                    &mdash; Base: <code class="code-inline">[Authorize]</code>. Review actions require <code class="code-inline">Admin</code> or <code class="code-inline">Reviewer</code> role.
                </p>

                <h3>Route Reference</h3>
                <table class="guide-table">
                    <thead><tr><th>Method</th><th>Route</th><th>Role</th><th>Purpose</th></tr></thead>
                    <tbody>
                        <tr><td><span class="route-method route-post">POST</span></td><td><code class="code-inline">/Submission/Submit</code></td><td>User</td><td>Submit report for review (computes completion level, creates snapshot)</td></tr>
                        <tr><td><span class="route-method route-post">POST</span></td><td><code class="code-inline">/Submission/Withdraw</code></td><td>User</td><td>Withdraw submission (only if status = Submitted)</td></tr>
                        <tr><td><span class="route-method route-get">GET</span></td><td><code class="code-inline">/Submission/Queue</code></td><td>Admin, Reviewer</td><td>Review queue with tabs: pending, my-reviews, revision, all</td></tr>
                        <tr><td><span class="route-method route-get">GET</span></td><td><code class="code-inline">/Submission/Review/{id}</code></td><td>Admin, Reviewer</td><td>Detailed review page (id = PublicId GUID)</td></tr>
                        <tr><td><span class="route-method route-post">POST</span></td><td><code class="code-inline">/Submission/Claim</code></td><td>Admin, Reviewer</td><td>Claim report (Submitted &rarr; UnderReview)</td></tr>
                        <tr><td><span class="route-method route-post">POST</span></td><td><code class="code-inline">/Submission/Unclaim</code></td><td>Admin, Reviewer</td><td>Release report back to queue</td></tr>
                        <tr><td><span class="route-method route-post">POST</span></td><td><code class="code-inline">/Submission/Validate</code></td><td>Admin, Reviewer</td><td>Approve report + generate PDF + create validation snapshot</td></tr>
                        <tr><td><span class="route-method route-post">POST</span></td><td><code class="code-inline">/Submission/Reject</code></td><td>Admin, Reviewer</td><td>Send back for revision with reason</td></tr>
                        <tr><td><span class="route-method route-post">POST</span></td><td><code class="code-inline">/Submission/Unlock</code></td><td>Admin</td><td>Unlock validated report (creates PreEditBackup snapshot)</td></tr>
                        <tr><td><span class="route-method route-post">POST</span></td><td><code class="code-inline">/Submission/AddNote</code></td><td>Admin, Reviewer</td><td>Add review note (type, stream reference, internal flag)</td></tr>
                        <tr><td><span class="route-method route-get">GET</span></td><td><code class="code-inline">/Submission/Notes</code></td><td>Admin, Reviewer</td><td>Fetch all notes for a report (JSON)</td></tr>
                        <tr><td><span class="route-method route-get">GET</span></td><td><code class="code-inline">/Submission/Validated</code></td><td>Admin, Reviewer</td><td>Library of approved reports</td></tr>
                        <tr><td><span class="route-method route-post">POST</span></td><td><code class="code-inline">/Submission/BulkValidate</code></td><td>Admin, Reviewer</td><td>Batch validate multiple reports</td></tr>
                        <tr><td><span class="route-method route-post">POST</span></td><td><code class="code-inline">/Submission/BulkAssign</code></td><td>Admin</td><td>Batch assign reviewer to multiple reports</td></tr>
                        <tr><td><span class="route-method route-get">GET</span></td><td><code class="code-inline">/Submission/Snapshot/{id}</code></td><td>Admin, Reviewer</td><td>View a historical snapshot</td></tr>
                        <tr><td><span class="route-method route-get">GET</span></td><td><code class="code-inline">/Submission/Artifact/{id}</code></td><td>Admin, Reviewer</td><td>Download or view generated PDF/Excel artifact</td></tr>
                    </tbody>
                </table>
            </section>

            <!-- 5. Services -->
            <section id="services" class="guide-section">
                <h2>
                    <span class="section-icon"><i class="bi bi-box"></i></span>
                    Services (Business Logic)
                </h2>
                <p>All services are registered as <code class="code-inline">Scoped</code> in <code class="code-inline">Program.cs</code>.</p>

                <h3>SubmissionService</h3>
                <p><span class="file-path"><i class="bi bi-file-code"></i> Services/SubmissionService.cs</span></p>
                <table class="guide-table">
                    <thead><tr><th>Method</th><th>Behavior</th></tr></thead>
                    <tbody>
                        <tr><td><code class="code-inline">SubmitForReview(id, userId)</code></td><td>Validates ownership, computes CompletionLevel, sets status to Submitted, creates snapshot</td></tr>
                        <tr><td><code class="code-inline">WithdrawSubmission(id, userId)</code></td><td>Reverts Submitted &rarr; Draft (only if not yet claimed)</td></tr>
                        <tr><td><code class="code-inline">ClaimForReview(id, reviewerUserId)</code></td><td>Sets status to UnderReview, assigns ReviewerUserId</td></tr>
                        <tr><td><code class="code-inline">UnclaimReview(id, reviewerUserId)</code></td><td>Returns to Submitted, clears reviewer assignment</td></tr>
                        <tr><td><code class="code-inline">AssignReviewer(id, reviewerUserId, adminUserId)</code></td><td>Admin-initiated reviewer assignment</td></tr>
                    </tbody>
                </table>

                <h4>Completion Level Algorithm</h4>
                <div class="code-block">
<span class="type">Full</span>    = hasAnyStream && hasCauses && hasRecommendations && hasPrioritization
<span class="type">Partial</span> = hasAnyStream
<span class="type">Metadata</span>= <span class="cm">// everything else (only title/location/financial data)</span>
                </div>

                <h3>ValidationService</h3>
                <p><span class="file-path"><i class="bi bi-file-code"></i> Services/ValidationService.cs</span></p>
                <table class="guide-table">
                    <thead><tr><th>Method</th><th>Behavior</th></tr></thead>
                    <tbody>
                        <tr><td><code class="code-inline">ValidateReport(id, userId, comment)</code></td><td>Status &rarr; Validated, creates snapshot, generates PDF artifact</td></tr>
                        <tr><td><code class="code-inline">RejectReport(id, userId, reason)</code></td><td>Status &rarr; NeedsRevision, stores RevisionReason, creates ReviewNote</td></tr>
                        <tr><td><code class="code-inline">UnlockForRevision(id, adminUserId, reason)</code></td><td>Validated &rarr; NeedsRevision, creates PreEditBackup snapshot</td></tr>
                        <tr><td><code class="code-inline">BulkValidate(ids[], userId)</code></td><td>Batch validate, returns success/failure counts</td></tr>
                    </tbody>
                </table>

                <h3>SnapshotService</h3>
                <p><span class="file-path"><i class="bi bi-file-code"></i> Services/SnapshotService.cs</span></p>
                <table class="guide-table">
                    <thead><tr><th>Method</th><th>Behavior</th></tr></thead>
                    <tbody>
                        <tr><td><code class="code-inline">CreateSnapshot(reportId, type, userId)</code></td><td>Serializes full report state to JSON snapshot</td></tr>
                        <tr><td><code class="code-inline">GetSnapshotsForReport(reportId)</code></td><td>Returns all snapshots ordered by creation date</td></tr>
                        <tr><td><code class="code-inline">BuildFormViewModelFromReport(report)</code></td><td>Converts report entity to form ViewModel for rendering</td></tr>
                    </tbody>
                </table>

                <h3>ArtifactService</h3>
                <p><span class="file-path"><i class="bi bi-file-code"></i> Services/ArtifactService.cs</span></p>
                <table class="guide-table">
                    <thead><tr><th>Method</th><th>Behavior</th></tr></thead>
                    <tbody>
                        <tr><td><code class="code-inline">GeneratePdfArtifact(reportId, snapshotId, userId)</code></td><td>Creates PDF using QuestPDF and stores as ReportArtifact</td></tr>
                        <tr><td><code class="code-inline">GetArtifactStream(artifactId)</code></td><td>Returns file stream, filename, and content type</td></tr>
                    </tbody>
                </table>
            </section>

