            <!-- 9. Audit System -->
            <section id="audit-system" class="guide-section">
                <h2>
                    <span class="section-icon"><i class="bi bi-journal-text"></i></span>
                    Audit System
                </h2>
                <p>Audit logging happens at two levels:</p>

                <h3>1. Automatic (SaveChangesAsync Override)</h3>
                <p><span class="file-path"><i class="bi bi-file-code"></i> Data/ApplicationDbContext.cs</span></p>
                <p>The <code class="code-inline">SaveChangesAsync()</code> override intercepts all <code class="code-inline">RosraReport</code> changes and creates <code class="code-inline">AuditLog</code> entries:</p>
                <table class="guide-table">
                    <thead><tr><th>Entity State</th><th>Action Logged</th></tr></thead>
                    <tbody>
                        <tr><td>Added</td><td><code class="code-inline">Created</code></td></tr>
                        <tr><td>Modified (IsDeleted changed)</td><td><code class="code-inline">Deleted</code> or <code class="code-inline">Restored</code></td></tr>
                        <tr><td>Modified (Status changed)</td><td><code class="code-inline">StatusChanged</code> with StatusFrom/StatusTo</td></tr>
                        <tr><td>Modified (other)</td><td><code class="code-inline">Updated</code> with changed property names</td></tr>
                        <tr><td>Deleted</td><td><code class="code-inline">PermanentlyDeleted</code></td></tr>
                    </tbody>
                </table>

                <h3>2. Manual (LogAuditAsync)</h3>
                <p><span class="file-path"><i class="bi bi-file-code"></i> Controllers/AdminController.cs</span></p>
                <p>Called explicitly for non-report entities:</p>
                <div class="code-block">
<span class="kw">await</span> <span class="fn">LogAuditAsync</span>(
    action:     <span class="str">"RoleAssigned"</span>,
    entityType: <span class="str">"User"</span>,
    entityId:   userId,
    details:    <span class="str">$"Role '{roleName}' assigned to {email}"</span>,
    statusFrom: <span class="kw">null</span>,
    statusTo:   <span class="kw">null</span>,
    reason:     <span class="kw">null</span>
);
                </div>

                <h3>Actions Logged</h3>
                <table class="guide-table">
                    <thead><tr><th>Action</th><th>Trigger</th></tr></thead>
                    <tbody>
                        <tr><td><code class="code-inline">RoleAssigned</code></td><td>Admin assigns role to user</td></tr>
                        <tr><td><code class="code-inline">RoleRemoved</code></td><td>Admin removes role from user</td></tr>
                        <tr><td><code class="code-inline">RoleCreated</code></td><td>Admin creates a new role</td></tr>
                        <tr><td><code class="code-inline">RoleDeleted</code></td><td>Admin deletes a role</td></tr>
                        <tr><td><code class="code-inline">UserActivated</code></td><td>Admin toggles user to active</td></tr>
                        <tr><td><code class="code-inline">UserDeactivated</code></td><td>Admin toggles user to inactive</td></tr>
                        <tr><td><code class="code-inline">Created</code></td><td>Report saved for the first time</td></tr>
                        <tr><td><code class="code-inline">Updated</code></td><td>Report modified</td></tr>
                        <tr><td><code class="code-inline">StatusChanged</code></td><td>Report status transitions (with from/to)</td></tr>
                        <tr><td><code class="code-inline">Deleted / Restored</code></td><td>Soft-delete toggle</td></tr>
                        <tr><td><code class="code-inline">PermanentlyDeleted</code></td><td>Hard-delete from trash</td></tr>
                    </tbody>
                </table>
            </section>

            <!-- 10. Data Upload -->
            <section id="data-upload" class="guide-section">
                <h2>
                    <span class="section-icon"><i class="bi bi-cloud-upload"></i></span>
                    Data Upload (CSV Import)
                </h2>

                <h3>Peer SNG Data</h3>
                <p>Route: <code class="code-inline">POST /Admin/UploadPeerSNGData</code></p>
                <h4>Expected CSV Format</h4>
                <div class="code-block">
SNG,OSR,GCP,Include
Baringo,<span class="num">321.4</span>,<span class="num">75459</span>,<span class="num">1</span>
Bomet,<span class="num">198.7</span>,<span class="num">62340</span>,<span class="num">1</span>
Nairobi,<span class="num">15200.5</span>,<span class="num">498230</span>,<span class="num">0</span>
                </div>
                <table class="guide-table">
                    <thead><tr><th>Column</th><th>Type</th><th>Description</th></tr></thead>
                    <tbody>
                        <tr><td>SNG</td><td>string</td><td>Subnational government name</td></tr>
                        <tr><td>OSR</td><td>decimal</td><td>Own-source revenue (millions)</td></tr>
                        <tr><td>GCP</td><td>decimal</td><td>Gross county product / GDP</td></tr>
                        <tr><td>Include</td><td>bool</td><td>1 or "true" to include in analysis</td></tr>
                    </tbody>
                </table>

